Package org.swisscheese.swisscheese.settings

Package for Objects responsible for setting and saving game settings into SwissCheese/settings folder.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameSettings
    This is a game settings object class that contains settings of the game that are used when the game is loaded from the StartMenu.
    GameSettingsManager
    This class serializes and deserializes GameSettings object to file.
